-God! What more do you need?

22:35.806 --> 22:37.006
You don't belong here.

22:37.073 --> 22:39.173
You shouldn't be here.
You don't fit in here!

22:39.306 --> 22:40.740
So just go!

22:43.539 --> 22:44.940
-You win, Hardin.

22:47.108 --> 22:48.208
You always do.

22:50.475 --> 22:51.541
-You'd know better than anyone.

23:22.415 --> 23:24.581
<i>-♪ I'm broken ♪</i>

23:24.616 --> 23:27.516
<i>♪ Tell you I'm fine ♪</i>

23:27.548 --> 23:29.050
