-You sure you don't want help?

23:47.887 --> 23:49.787
-No, it's just
a couple of things.

23:49.887 --> 23:54.355
I got most of it
before Seattle anyway. So.

23:54.455 --> 23:55.822
-Okay.

23:57.655 --> 23:58.522
Don't say I didn't ask.

23:58.655 --> 23:59.722
Uh-hmm.

23:59.755 --> 24:01.890
<i>-♪ Oh please come pick me up ♪</i>

24:01.923 --> 24:04.723
<i>♪ From my lowest</i>
<i>Take me higher ♪</i>

24:04.756 --> 24:06.190
<i>♪ Can you see me ♪</i>

24:06.223 --> 24:08.891
<i>♪ Through the ashes</i>
<i>And the smoke ♪</i>

